flowchart TD
    A([Start: User wants to visit a page]) --> B[Enter URL in input field]
    B --> C{Is URL syntactically valid?}
    C -- No --> D[Display Invalid URL error]
    D --> Z([End])
    C -- Yes --> E[Normalize URL with https:// prefix]
    E --> F{Does URL match current page exactly?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Display Duplicate Visit warning]
    G --> Z
    F -- No --> H{Is current node not the tail?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Discard all forward nodes]
    I --> J[Create new Node]
    H -- No --> J
    J --> K[Link new node after current: current.next = new, new.prev = current]
    K --> L[Move tail and current pointers to new node]
    L --> M[Persist full list snapshot to SQLite]
    M --> N[Re-render Streamlit UI]
    N --> Z
